fmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Brazen+Brides+Grotesque+Daughters+Treacherous+Mothers+by+Felicity+Collins+%28Bakhtin%2C+308-317%29&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sensesofcinema.com%2F2002%2F23%2Fwomen_funny_oz%2F&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AGrotesque+body\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation journal\">Boje, David M. (March 2004). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://peaceaware.com/McD/papers/Lyon%20proceedings%20Boje%202994%20Grotesque%20Method%20.pdf\">\"Grotesque Method\"</a> <span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(PDF)</span>. <i>Proceedings of First International Co-sponsored Conference, Research methods Division, Academy of Management: Crossing Frontiers in Quantitative and Qualitative Research methods</i>. <b>2</b>: 1085\u20131114.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Proceedings+of+First+International+Co-sponsored+Conference%2C+Research+methods+Division%2C+Academy+of+Management%3A+Crossing+Frontiers+in+Quantitative+and+Qualitative+Research+methods.&amp;rft.atitle=Grotesque+Method&amp;rft.volume=2&amp;rft.pages=1085-1114&amp;rft.date=2004-03&amp;rft.aulast=Boje&amp;rft.aufirst=David+M.&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fpeaceaware.com%2FMcD%2Fpapers%2FLyon%2520proceedings%2520Boje%25202994%2520Grotesque%2520Method%2520.pdf&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AGrotesque+body\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-:0-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">^ <a href=\"#cite_ref-:0_7-0\"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-:0_7-1\"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation book\">Wright, Thomas (1865).